            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Buchstabenhöhe: IRT 694: 3-4; IRT 529: 3.5-8. Datierung: IRT 694: late III century; IRT 529: late IV - early V century. Interpunktion: IRT 694 u. IRT 529: Palmette. Base used four times: two earlier texts erased, then IRT 694 and lastly IRT 529.</p>
